{"tid":1391470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港總商會會出聲？","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:37:44.000Z","uid":295444,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2daea1470dffe578d89f565960cf6b9ecb1a262","tid":1391470,"uid":295444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"大家有冇留意點解香港總商會會出聲？佢地係22/7出聲明。係因為元朗事件之後的一日。係D生意佬都好撚驚會帶來經濟損失才發聲明。其實經濟牌真係最無人命傷亡的最有效辦法。如果香港經濟崩潰，就再沒有任何利用價值。這才是中共最不希望見到的。<br />\n<br />\n之前嗰啲沽港元/換美金/中資提款其實民間做係冇用，要大I bank 夾埋沽先有用。所以暫時最有效真係長期罷工、罷稅。順住呢條水，大家有乜其他計？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chamber.org.hk/en/media/press-releases_detail.aspx?ID=3638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chamber.org.hk%2Fen%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases_detail.aspx%3FID%3D3638&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=e20b6534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chamber.org.hk/en/media/press-releases_detail.aspx?ID=3638</a>"},{"pid":"901ce2c0e7da0cbc7e879c30c4b340739c69fc8e","tid":1391470,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"減暴力，長期玩，才有用。"},{"pid":"9f030be9d3a0601d6f9837a939558df079e0f32b","tid":1391470,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要說&quot;推&quot;, <br />\n<br />\n試著說：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hf7ppz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hf7ppz.png&h=37691996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/rppcCsL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrppcCsL.png&h=cf9768dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkS5Vwe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li